source.title: The Great Flood: Evidence of Advanced Civilization Destruction
source.description:
The Great Flood: Evidence of Advanced Civilization Destruction

Flood myths are often treated as moral allegories or religious symbolism. But what if they preserve something more? Across continents and time periods, different cultures recall a catastrophic deluge, a moment that reset history, not just spiritually, but physically. These stories, told with striking similarity, raise a question that modern science rarely confronts: Could a flood have marked the end of a forgotten chapter in the development of intelligent life on Earth? Could a flood have wiped out an ancient civilization before us?

In this episode of Secret Origins, we explore that possibility and what the floodwaters really covered. Sometimes what we dismiss as myth may be memory. And sometimes, what remains hidden isnâ€™t lost, just unacknowledged.

SUBSCRIBE for more documentaries: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCxAt0KkZZUxgG3yxl-WDM2A/?sub_confirmation=1
